  <brief_title>Is the 4MGS a Useful Outcome Measure Post-PPCI</brief_title>
  <official_title>Is the Four Metre Gait Speed a Useful Outcome Measure in Patients With Acute Myocardial Infarction After Primary Percutaneous Coronary Intervention?</official_title>
  <sponsors>
